Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡鬧 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄胡鬧 的Everyday (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是否越來越接近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼反應 沒寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我在意的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能量活力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,「女孩子就應該這樣那樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想 願望 都只是空想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 絞盡腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想一直贏過你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要反擊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,壓倒性的完全勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因為喜歡 所以為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想破壞一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Night Date)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 只有你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還不清楚 青澀的春日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,清醒的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Night Date)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是愛的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡鬧 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要執著 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄胡鬧Everyday (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們大聲喧囂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(學長，要不要去祭典啊？)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道有沒有賣蘋果糖葫蘆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-今天 好像有夏日祭典\N-希望有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 要不要去祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看你可憐\N我就大發慈悲的邀請你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,應該會一如往常地硬拉我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,K.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Round Two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾 我也該…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,主動… 邀請她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 真的好噁心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噁心噁心好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噁心噁心 噁心噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我幹嘛邀請她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,K.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(棉花糖)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我很閒 所以來逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,買完炒麵就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,發現學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,學長也會來祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好意外喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,意外的海蟑螂 意外海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱著能偶遇小早的想法\N就過來閒晃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,閒晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她有社團活動 所以不能來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-那…\N-別走啊 難得的祭典耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的 只是路過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出剛才抽到的獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到學長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你陪練到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 反正最近我也沒怎麼練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 今天好像有祭典喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點晚了 但要不要去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你們傳給長瀞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 她搞不好會來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我家的寵物被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是寵物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞有社團活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,突然找她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她才不會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉… 社團活動還沒結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 社團提早結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很閒 所以來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,戴著項圈 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 超好笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 快解開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好玩 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,學長是我們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想搶的話就跟我們決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我無所謂學長的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但我接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(射擊)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,2對2的雙人賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,得到獎品多的那隊獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 不要扯後腿喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要比嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我打中了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要瞄準更上面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我有瞄準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為學長不會來祭典這種場合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是出來轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜 沒打中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在等我… 主動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,邀請你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想跟別人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,應該要自己主動去邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你們仔細看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻魷魚娃的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以質量來說我們壓倒性獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不足以彌補數量上的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 小吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是那隻魷魚娃很稀有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得你在收集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小早我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,居然使出收買招式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到學長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快解開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小心別再被抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是野生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,來都來了 就到處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(不要欺負我，長瀞同學)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(好像在約會喔，學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,給我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-簡直…\N-接著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在約會對吧 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼約會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這應該是情侶之間做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能跟學長約會\N笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別摸了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要 乾脆牽個手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,已經開始放煙火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 去看煙火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要推我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的煙火很漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,會在空中放很多大型煙火\N砰砰砰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我看過了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,國小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太久以前了吧 你是家裡蹲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你很煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(煙火大會 會場在前方10公尺)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,隊伍都沒在前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得以前看花火時…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞 往那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不快點的話就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,學長你打算幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得是那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 把我帶到沒人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起 小時候在這裡看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不過啊學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,約會時把女孩子帶到陰暗角落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不太好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼陰暗角落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人都會起防備心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還硬拉著我的手唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,害我以為你要做什麼糟糕的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕喔 糟糕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,處男學長好糟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕喔 糟糕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-又拿處男的事嘲笑我\N-處男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-不過\N糟糕喔 糟糕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道這傢伙也挺害羞的\N-處男 糟糕唷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的事是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的事 就是糟糕的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小事你應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不知道 請具體說明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細地說明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,突然強行抱住人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,親親之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這該不會就是學長的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,反正處男不可能辦到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,處男學長怎麼可能強吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就辦得到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,稀鬆平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,又放了一顆好大的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶 好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,難得的祭典 早知道就穿浴衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想跟別人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,應該要自己主動去邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下… 下次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明年… 要不要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,學長也要穿浴衣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,男生不用穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 跟我穿情侶裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,情侶裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,情侶裝… 浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要跟學長穿情侶裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太噁心了 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(我們回去吧，學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,新學期第一天 真提不起幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,回家繼續打電玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-上禮拜沒跟你告白嗎\N-這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對方是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是三班的星野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-他不是小葵的男朋友嗎\N-是長瀞家族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-散發著難以接近的氛圍\N-笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友人數增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最近 她經常… 來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們果然還是不同世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,比方說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,生活在黑暗洞穴中的鼴鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然露出地面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,卻剛好是美洲虎的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一來就裝模作樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,練習真的超累的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們明明就沒去社團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,社長都氣炸了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 社長超可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真熟練
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他們自然而然地融入女生團體中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比起我這種人 還是他們比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小早 我們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證一定很好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不想單獨跟他去玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雙雙對對 小吉也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好 就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別拒絕嘛\N反正在這裡聊天也很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,走嘛走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到車站再決定去哪玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊 可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是學長耶 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲在那裡幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 我聽不到耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 有種再大聲說一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回去吧 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,丟下他們好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒差吧 他們太煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到學長會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是畫漫畫的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,對 他畫了很糟糕的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我偶爾會畫漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是糟糕的題材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,學長不用說謊喔 色色漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟喔 色色漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像散發著獨特的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 色色漫畫的氣息\N從這頭毛茸茸的頭髮中飄散出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻別被色色漫畫傳染喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小心色色漫畫氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算每天聊個沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,話題仍聊不完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天遇到的所有事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,最近(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,比以前(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,增加許多(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一如往常 放學後在美術室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻笑打鬧 就跟平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸地變化 描繪著校園的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,明天比今天 變得更加繽紛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的反省重點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,學長為何不主動邀請我去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,其實你超想去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不能總是等待天上掉下來的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還好有一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好噁
